  dialogue:
  - My, what do we have here. Some fine pastries.
  - I'll take one of your purple donuts. Yes, just one will do.
  responses:
  - responseText: I didn't know wolves ate donuts too.
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 77a01ee0fb7f33b4aa158a0d8f9f62ff, type: 2}
    customerExpression: {fileID: 1466652921, guid: 94c521f98e039a249820711f4a040476, type: 3}
  - responseText: Are you suffering from male pattern balding?
